lminus(25.10)                                                    lminus(25.10)

Name lminus - Subtracts the specified elements in the second list (list2) from
       the first specified list (list1)
Syntax
Parameters  -exact  Searches  for  an exact match. <list1>  Specifies the list
       from which elements must be removed. <list2> Specifies the list of ele-
       ments to be subtracted.
